{"id": "1409743736296050732", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "953257370115522590", "author_name": "_renari", "author_bot": false, "content": "ジェンキンとトゥルーは共に行動値を食べるキャラなのであまり推奨ではありませんが、無理くり組むなら耐久のシレストサンガーカエクスから選択ですね", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T03:38:18.505000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
