{"id": "1409805979058442252", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "248046998031302656", "author_name": "makino23", "author_bot": false, "content": "ティンクトは敵の力ダウン札があって\nコレがデフォルト2コストの保持\n1凸で準備を獲得するようになるので\n「次のターン使おっかな〜」って構えている間にコストが安くなっていく。強い凸\n\nウインクルは2凸で3行動力の防御札にデカめの反撃がついて\n結構良好。無くても強いけど\n\nサンガーは1凸で全体軟化を防御しながら打てるようになって強まる。無くても強いけど\n\nトゥルーは123凸全部強い", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T07:45:38.336000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["353904831959924737"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1409785861440143400", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409852927157342361", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "355994607147941888", "author_name": "akapan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "4-5で行き詰まりましたorz\nプレイヤーレベル31\n下記のパーティで今まで進行してます。有識者の方アドバイスあればお願いしたいです。", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T10:52:11.635000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-26T10:52:37.454000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1409852926930718730", "filename": "IMG_5320.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1969580, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1409852926930718730/IMG_5320.png?ex=6a34769b&is=6a33251b&hm=a4d164ad0e1e491e0e4ba167d74ad00697e426bd091c848deb59b65634c272fd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409866957620248579", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "248046998031302656", "author_name": "makino23", "author_bot": false, "content": "顔ぶれは良好なので、先に闇の境界をクリアしてレベルキャップを50にする\nか\n伝家の宝刀、超次元/深海に乗り換える\n辺りが手っ取り早いかしら", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T11:47:56.758000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409869302449967165", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "811931498164387850", "author_name": "a8789", "author_bot": false, "content": "ナウティララモンナを入れ替える。超次元入れるのがよさそ", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T11:57:15.809000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
