{"id": "1409878016347078666", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "355994607147941888", "author_name": "akapan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "宝刀ってアイテムですか？", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T12:31:53.364000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["248046998031302656"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1409866957620248579", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409878172039909486", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "248046998031302656", "author_name": "makino23", "author_bot": false, "content": "わかりにくい表現ですいません\nめっちゃつよい、超次元/深海に乗り換えるって提案です", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T12:32:30.484000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1409878321704996966", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "355994607147941888", "author_name": "akapan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "あ、そうなんですね！\nちなみに超次元のキャラはわかりますか？", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T12:33:06.167000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["248046998031302656"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1409878172039909486", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
