{"id": "1409878837377892466", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1342589561968263239", "author_name": "maru045800", "author_bot": false, "content": "昨日から始めた無課金勢です。\n2-6辺りにいますが、こちらの編成だと何処かで行き詰まったりしますか…？\n回復役無し編成なので少し不安です。", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T12:35:09.113000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1409878836727910450", "filename": "Screenshot_20250826_213322.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 137315, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1409878836727910450/Screenshot_20250826_213322.jpg?ex=6a348ebc&is=6a333d3c&hm=baab7268ab0e525dd7bfa51a76073ee6cf87168935879b1e303119b839e5d34e&"}, {"id": "1409878837181026344", "filename": "Screenshot_20250826_213337.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 180515, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1409878837181026344/Screenshot_20250826_213337.jpg?ex=6a348ebd&is=6a333d3d&hm=447f6c792a345d440f88860cfbc223e9ceab021946b489b71bfe1fe05856606f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
